00:02:47.130 --> 00:02:49.490
economic history, social history.

00:02:49.490 --> 00:02:51.770
He's written about
the Colonial north,

00:02:51.770 --> 00:02:53.420
he's written about
the Colonial south,

00:02:53.420 --> 00:02:55.590
he's written about everything.

00:02:55.590 --> 00:03:00.310
And it's just been a great
