00:47:18.040 --> 00:47:21.030
it's still a tax that
we didn't vote on.

00:47:21.030 --> 00:47:26.150
And so it's on principle
not acceptable.

00:47:26.150 --> 00:47:32.280
But I don't -- but again,
my point was all that aside,

00:47:32.280 --> 00:47:36.970
it was the British reaction
sending General Gage and thousands

00:47:36.970 --> 00:47:42.740
of soldiers to Boston and closing
Massachusetts to all commerce,

00:47:42.740 --> 00:47:44.570
and closing all town meetings

00:47:44.570 --> 00:47:48.970
that by then had a 200 year
history of self-government.

00:47:48.970 --> 00:47:50.590
It's exactly the same thing --

00:47:50.590 --> 00:47:53.110
I'm looking at my Irish
friend back there.

00:47:53.110 --> 00:47:56.860
It's exactly the same thing the
Brits after the Eastern rising.

00:47:56.860 --> 00:47:59.820
The Easter rising, most Irish
people felt were a bunch

00:47:59.820 --> 00:48:01.760
of nutters, you know.

00:48:01.760 --> 00:48:04.760
And they probably were.

00:48:04.760 --> 00:48:11.860
But it was the execution day after
day after day, and the humiliation

00:48:11.860 --> 00:48:19.150
of the Irish people that turned
a weak protest into a rebellion.

00:48:19.150 --> 00:48:21.090
Same thing happened here.

00:48:21.090 --> 00:48:31.140
Nut cases were made
martyrs to the people.

00:48:31.140 --> 00:48:34.760
Yes? He's going to give
you a speaker dinger.

00:48:34.760 --> 00:48:39.000
