00:52:47.280 --> 00:52:50.610
Ninety-six had some bad
times during the war.

00:52:50.610 --> 00:52:56.610
And there was a man that
had created real havoc

00:52:56.610 --> 00:53:00.000
who had the interesting
name of Matthew Love.

00:53:00.000 --> 00:53:02.020
That was the last thing
I'd associate

00:53:02.020 --> 00:53:05.050
with Matthew, because
he was a killer.

00:53:05.050 --> 00:53:08.720
But the war ended and the
peace treaty was announced

00:53:08.720 --> 00:53:11.900 position:56%
and he showed back up in Ninety-six.

00:53:11.900 --> 00:53:13.690
Said, I'm here guys.

00:53:13.690 --> 00:53:15.420
Back home.

00:53:15.420 --> 00:53:18.240
The locals said, oh boy.

00:53:18.240 --> 00:53:23.410
They locked him up in jail and they
waited for the judge to come up --

00:53:23.410 --> 00:53:26.880
because there was -- judge's
